description.narrative: (USAID Global Health (GH)): Data.FI will work with a range of stakeholders to support host country governments to further enhance existing health information systems platforms to inform management responses to well-defined gaps in health programming. This mechanism will bolster data quality, utilize available data, perform analyses and translate findings in a way that facilitates rapid, efficient implementation, as well as generate information to provide rationales for costs and outcomes for scale-up and maintenance.
